query:
ALTER TABLE performance_groups 
ADD COLUMN daypartingEnabled TINYINT DEFAULT 1,
ADD COLUMN daypartingStrategy ENUM('performance_based','equal','custom') DEFAULT 'performance_based',
ADD COLUMN daypartingAutoAdjust TINYINT DEFAULT 1,
ADD COLUMN daypartingMinBudgetPercent INT DEFAULT 50,
ADD COLUMN daypartingMaxBudgetPercent INT DEFAULT 150,
ADD COLUMN daypartingReserveBudget DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN daypartingLastAnalysis TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN daypartingLastExecution TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN keywordAutoEnabled TINYINT DEFAULT 1,
ADD COLUMN keywordAutoPauseEnabled TINYINT DEFAULT 1,
ADD COLUMN keywordAutoEnableEnabled TINYINT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN keywordPauseMinSpend DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT 10,
ADD COLUMN keywordPauseMaxAcos DECIMAL(5,2) DEFAULT 50,
ADD COLUMN keywordLastAutoExecution TIMESTAMP NULL;
